            {
                "category": "summary",
                "text": "NVIDIA has released a software update for NVIDIA\u00ae NemoClaw.&nbsp;<div>To protect your system, clone or update this software to v0.0.18 from the <a href=\"https://github.com/NVIDIA/NemoClaw\">NVIDIA/NemoClaw</a> GitHub repo.</div>",
